➜【星连文学社】凤萍（香港）：《读心经，心的诉说》
http://www.sohu.com/a/412131837_100115135	32854
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200808/b85a351a8ad14a99a32c59582d7cd83f.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>《读心经，心的诉说》</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong> 文/凤萍（香港）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">静静抱住你</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">读你，到日月无光</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在你的怀里起伏不定</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">掩而不听那尘世喧嚣</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>你让我百读不厌</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>如同海水不可斗量</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>为你付出、只想心有共鸣</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>在梦中继续与你窃窃私语</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">爱你给我心的放纵</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">时光流淌，禅音入血液中</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">耳畔经幡飘扬的歌声</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">伴我此生走过人间的旅程</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200808/be205debb2d54439a53c178a0fb9fd76.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
