➜【星连文学社】江西诗人时差先生：陌生的沙漠
http://www.sohu.com/a/412132517_100115135	33175
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200808/88b400d4debe43a1b8d9d9095d19430a.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>陌生的沙漠</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong> 文/时差先生</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"> 天空 </p>
<p class="ql-align-center"> 嘶吼的</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"> 茫然失神</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"> <strong>气流</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong> 涌烫的</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong> 吞噬时空</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"> 砂砾</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"> 在</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"> 燃烧着云朵</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"> <strong>风暴</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong> 是狂野的</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong> 在地狱繁殖</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"> 呵</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"> 我的心被撕裂成</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"> 明天的太阳</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"> <strong>谱写着一部</strong></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
