➜【星连文学社】彩虹：两个水鸟
http://www.sohu.com/a/412132785_100115135	33503
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200808/9436bc4c45d64598b4be068869d0c4bd.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>两个水鸟</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文/彩虹</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">黄昏中的雨亭</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一抹蓝，一抹白，一抹绿</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">立在水中央，苍茫素墨</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">好似渔歌唱晚</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">柳叶风骚</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>深绿荷叶高低起伏</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>左拥右抱，荷花高傲的</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>吐芳</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>红如玫瑰，鲜如桃花，白</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>沾不着水灵</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>水鸟垂爱，悠闲</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>悠闲陪着</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">踏着水莲花似的</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在浮萍，菱角上</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">走着，走着……</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">小鱼们嚼着口香糖</p>            <div class="lookall-box">
